==Notes==
* The [[obese tourist]] and [[terrifying robot]] only appear after the player boards the space cruise ship during the [[Future]] quest. After the quest is over, the monsters can continue to appear in the zone.
* The choice adventures [[Savior Faire]] and [[The Savorier Savior]] (and subsequently the other choice adventures triggered by them) do not occur while the player is on the [[Future]] quest.
* It is possible to access this part of KoL through teleportitis.
* See the [[Seaside Megalopolis Noncombats]] page for an overview of non-quest choice adventures.
